ygData.messageBody:
The exp was unbelievable....I have gained almost 2 bubbles off 4 pieces at
lvl 30-33....b4 I realized I was gaining so much exp I kinda dreaded running
all the way over there to SK.....but I made more exp in like 2 mins than you
can make in a night :-)

Yeah, but in my case over half bub per completion... quite a
nice surprise.
